                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/c.ryouu/">Sandy</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-12-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实“镜中我”的雏形在斯密的《道德情操论》中即有涉及（那时斯密还是以政治哲学而非经济学著称），卢梭也有述及，但都没有像库利这样上升为核心概念、且把整个过程论述的如此完备。很简单的范式，我们甚至会发觉儿时即有类似雏形，却能深入浅出，此谓大师。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1090433131">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1090433131" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1090433131" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1090433131">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shichalo1990/">含容笃</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-09-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">库里吧，就是啰里八嗦的。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="787615804">
